he Tagesarbeit.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 4aAnwalt. 4aEigentümerversammlung. 4aSondernutzungsrechte. 4aVerwaltungsbeirat. 4aWEG. 4aWohnungseigentum. 4aWohnungseigentumsrecht. 7aLAW / Civil Law.2bisacsh1 aBecker, Matthias, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aFelz, Sebastian, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aGantert, Ulrike, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aHogenschurz, Johannes, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aHäublein, Martin, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aKöhler, Wilfried J., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aKöhler, Wilfried J., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aLeppla, Sebastian, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aMaier, Markus, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aOtt, Andreas, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aPeter, Michael, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aScheuer, Daniela, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aTank, Susanne, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aWolicki, Michael, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut40uhttps://doi.org/10.9785/978350438659740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783504386597423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783504386597/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles